Q1.  Time Complexity
------------------------------------------
What is the time complexity of heap sort ?
------------------------------------------
Options
This problem has only one correct answer:-
1. O(n)
2. O(logn)
3. O(nlogn) 
4. O(n^2)
Answer(3)

******************************************

Q2. Space Complexity
------------------------------------------
What is the space complexity of in-place heap sort? 
------------------------------------------
Options
This problem has only one correct answer:-
1. O(n)
2. O(1) 
3. O(logn)
4. O(nlogn)
Answer(2)

******************************************

Q3.  Time Complexity
------------------------------------------
What is the time complexity of heapify and building a heap?
------------------------------------------
Options
This problem has only one correct answer:-
1. O(n) and O(n)
2. O(n) and O(logn)
3. O(logn) and O(logn)
4. O(logn) and O(n) 
Answer(4)

******************************************
